Randomized Trial of Pleural Fluid Drainage Frequency in Patients with Malignant 
Pleural Effusions. The ASAP Trial.

Wahidi MM(1), Reddy C(2), Yarmus L(3), Feller-Kopman D(3), Musani A(4), Shepherd 
